No, connect_object() would only remove the signal widget. It would still pass the rest of parameters, e.g.:
$drawrea->connect_object('button_press_event', 'process');
function process($event) { /* only $event is passed */ }
$drawrea->connect_simple('button_press_event', 'process_simple');
function process_simple() { /* nothing is passed */ }
-Andrei
