Hi

I just did a completely new checkout and came across a problem with
windows line endings again in the generator scripts. This patch fixes
the problem.


diff -u -w -b -r1.28 override.php
--- override.php        4 Sep 2005 06:02:27 -0000       1.28
+++ override.php        17 Sep 2005 05:35:30 -0000
@@ -92,9 +92,11 @@

     function _parse_block($block, $blocklineno, $file_name)
     {
-        if (strpos($block, "\n"))
-            list($line, $rest) = explode("\n", $block, 2);
-        else {
+        if (strpos($block, "\n")) {
+             $test = preg_split('/\r\n|\n/',ltrim($block));
+             $line = array_shift($test);
+             $rest = implode("\n",$test);
+         } else {
             $line = $block;
             $rest = '';
         }

