assertion `GTK_IS_ADJUSTMENT (adjustment)' failed

If I don't pass an GtkAdjustment





Hope this help to improve php-gtk2



See you



Nicolas.







Here the sample script :



<?

if (!class_exists('gtk'))

   dl( 'php_gtk2.' . (strstr( PHP_OS, 'WIN') ? 'dll' : 'so'));



$wd = new GtkWindow(GTK_WINDOW_TOPLEVEL);



$adj = new GtkAdjustment(0, 0, 100, 1, 10, 0);

$progress = new GtkProgressBar($adj);



$progress->set_size_request(360, 20);

$wd->add($progress);

$wd->show_all();





function changebar() {

  global $pourcent, $progress, $adj;

  if ($pourcent == 100)

     $pourcent = 0;

  else

     $pourcent++;



  $adj->set_value($pourcent);

  $progress->set_value($pourcent);

  Gtk::timeout_add(1000, changebar);

  echo "change to $pourcent\n";

}



Gtk::timeout_add(1000, changebar);





Gtk::main();

?>





