Hi,

in addition to gtk_tree_store* I've added 
gtk_tree_model_get_iter_from_string which allowed me to implement 
editable cells in a tree:

[...]
$cell = new GtkCellRendererText;
$cell->set_data("column", 1);
$cell->connect("edited", "cell_edited", $store);
[...]
function cell_edited($cell, $path, $newText, $store) {
   $column = $cell->get_data("column");
   $iter = $store->get_iter_from_string($path);
   $store->set($iter, $column, $newText);
}
[...]

Since the whole GtkTreePath support is missing, get_iter_from_string 
seems the way of least ressistance to me.

- Markus

