Apparently you are correct. I was able to reproduce it by adding 
another try..catch to your func0().

   try {
     $xml = new SimpleXMLElement('asdf');
   } catch (Exception $e) {
       echo $e->getMessage() . "\n";
       echo $e->getTraceAsString() . "\n";
   }

And it came out the same. You may wish to report this as a bug.

