Hi

Here is a combined UiManager and GtkCalendar patch for gtk2
I have added a fourth value to the array returned by
GtkCalendar::get_date() which is a string suitable for use in the php
strtotime() function (ie. '2005-12-10')

The month I have left in the 0-11 format to match the rest of the
calendar functions.

The UiMangager functions I provided before were missing  NOT_STATIC_METHOD();

Hope this helps.

-- 

Tom                          
